{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "tool_call_update", "toolCallId": "call_cd15ee2e9e56456f8f5790f5", "status": "completed", "content": [{"type": "content", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "Web search results for \"Qwen Code settings.json configuration documentation\" (via DashScope):\n\n1. **Qwen Code Configuration - zdoc**\n   Qwen Code uses JSON settings files for persistent configuration. There are four locations for these files: System defaults file: Location: /etc/\n   Source: https://www.zdoc.app/en/QwenLM/qwen-code/blob/main/docs/cli/configuration.md\n   Relevance: 108%\n   Published: 2025-12-03 00:00:00\n\n2. **Better configuration and documentation · Issue #1015**\n   qwen/settings.json is a bit weird. Telling users to put a .env file in their code directory, but at the same time warning them not to commit is\n   Source: https://github.com/QwenLM/qwen-code/issues/1015\n   Relevance: 98%\n   Published: 2025-11-11 00:00:00\n\n3. **Qwen Code - ToolUniverse Documentation**\n   Add the ToolUniverse MCP server configuration to your Qwen settings settings.json . Note: Edit the JSON in your system terminal/editor. Basic Configuration: {\n   Source: https://zitniklab.hms.harvard.edu/ToolUniverse/guide/building_ai_scientists/qwen_code.html\n   Relevance: 86%\n\n4. **Qwen/qwen-code - 鲸智社区·大模型公共服务平台**\n   Configure Session Token Limit. Create or edit .qwen/settings.json in  For detailed authentication setup, see the authentication guide.\n   Source: https://aihub.caict.ac.cn/codes/Qwen/qwen-code\n   Relevance: 84%\n   Published: 2025-08-25 00:00:00\n\n5. **Qwen Code Configuration Guide**\n   Configure your MCP client to connect with your CloudBase environment. Step 1: Configure CloudBase MCP. Or add this configuration to .qwen/settings.json : json.\n   Source: https://docs.cloudbase.net/en/ai/cloudbase-ai-toolkit/ide-setup/qwen-code\n   Relevance: 79%\n\n*Note: For detailed content from any source above, use the web_fetch tool with the URL.*"}}], "serverName": "local", "toolName": "unknown"}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:51:32.662640Z"}
