{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "工具调用。\n- **用法**: `qwen --yolo`\n\n### 16. `--approval-mode <mode>`\n- **用途**: 设置工具调用的批准模式。\n- **取值**:\n  - `"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:07.630715Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "plan`: 仅分析——不修改文件或执行命令。\n  - `default`: 需要批准文件编辑或 shell 命令（默认行为）。\n  - `auto-edit`: 自动批准编辑工具（edit、write_file），"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:08.032560Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "同时提示批准其他工具。\n  - `yolo`: 自动批准所有工具调用（等同于 --yolo）。\n- **用法**: `qwen --approval-mode <mode>`\n- **注意**: 不能与 --y"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:08.326334Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "olo 同时使用。对于新的统一方法，请使用 --approval-mode=yolo 而非 --yolo。\n- **示例**: `qwen --approval-mode auto-edit`\n\n### 1"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:08.690661Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "7. `--allowed-tools <tool1,tool2,...>`\n- **用途**: 一个逗号分隔的工具名称列表，这些工具将绕过确认对话框。\n- **用法**: `qwen --allowed-tools "}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:09.073583Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "<tool1,tool2,...>`\n- **示例**: `qwen --allowed-tools \"Shell(git status)\"`\n\n### 18. `--telemetry`\n- **用途**:"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:09.368394Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": " 启用遥测。\n- **用法**: `qwen --telemetry`\n\n### 19. `--telemetry-target`\n- **用途**: 设置遥测目标。\n- **用法**: `qwen --telemetry"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:09.696730Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "-target <target>`\n\n### 20. `--telemetry-otlp-endpoint`\n- **用途**: 设置遥测的 OTLP 端点。\n- **用法**: `qwen --telemetry"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:11.677430Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "-otlp-endpoint <endpoint>`\n\n### 21. `--telemetry-otlp-protocol`\n- **用途**: 设置遥测的 OTLP 协议（grpc 或 http）。"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:12.010716Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "默认为 grpc。\n- **用法**: `qwen --telemetry-otlp-protocol <protocol>`\n\n### 22. `--telemetry-log-prompts`\n- **"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:12.644444Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "用途**: 启用遥测的提示词记录。\n- **用法**: `qwen --telemetry-log-prompts`\n\n### 23. `--checkpointing`\n- **用途**: 启用检查点"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:12.828174Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "。\n- **用法**: `qwen --checkpointing`\n\n### 24. `--extensions <extension_name ...>` 或 `-e <extension_name ..."}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:13.052998Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": ">`\n- **用途**: 指定会话要使用的扩展列表。如果未提供，则使用所有可用扩展。\n- **用法**: `qwen -e <extension_name> -e <extension_name>`\n-"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:13.586231Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": " **示例**: `qwen -e my-extension -e my-other-extension`\n- **特殊用法**: 使用特殊术语 `qwen -e none` 来禁用所有扩展。\n\n### 25"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:13.954736Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": ". `--list-extensions` 或 `-l`\n- **用途**: 列出所有可用扩展并退出。\n- **用法**: `qwen --list-extensions`\n\n### 26. `--proxy"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:14.165484Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "`\n- **用途**: 为 CLI 设置代理。\n- **用法**: `qwen --proxy <proxy_url>`\n- **示例**: `qwen --proxy http://localhost"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:14.427202Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": ":7890`\n\n### 27. `--include-directories <dir1,dir2,...>`\n- **用途**: 在工作空间中包含额外的目录以支持多目录。\n- **说明**: 可以多次"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:14.834083Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "指定或以逗号分隔的值提供。最多可添加 5 个目录。\n- **用法**: `qwen --include-directories <dir1,dir2,...>`\n- **示例**: \n  - `qwen --include"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:15.408400Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "-directories /path/to/project1,/path/to/project2`\n  - `qwen --include-directories /path/to/project1 --include-directories"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:16.003943Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": " /path/to/project2`\n\n### 28. `--screen-reader`\n- **用途**: 启用屏幕阅读器模式，调整 TUI 以更好地兼容屏幕阅读器。\n- **用法**: `qwen"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:16.445635Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": " --screen-reader`\n\n### 29. `--version`\n- **用途**: 显示 CLI 的版本。\n- **用法**: `qwen --version`\n\n### 30. `--open"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:16.672521Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "ai-logging`\n- **用途**: 启用 OpenAI API 调用的日志记录，用于调试和分析。此标志会覆盖 settings.json 中的 enableOpenAILogging 设置。\n- **用"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:16.949916Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "法**: `qwen --openai-logging`\n\n### 31. `--openai-logging-dir <directory>`\n- **用途**: 为 OpenAI API 日志设置自定义目录"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:17.238055Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "路径。此标志会覆盖 settings.json 中的 openAILoggingDir 设置。\n- **说明**: 支持绝对路径、相对路径和 ~ 扩展。\n- **用法**: `qwen --openai"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:17.547864Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "-logging-dir <directory>`\n- **示例**: `qwen --openai-logging-dir \"~/qwen-logs\" --openai-logging`\n\n### 3"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:17.855541Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "2. `--tavily-api-key <api_key>`\n- **用途**: 为此会话的网页搜索功能设置 Tavily API 密钥。\n- **用法**: `qwen --tavily-api-key"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:19.201365Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": " <api_key>`\n- **示例**: `qwen --tavily-api-key tvly-your-api-key-here`\n\n## 配置层级\n\n配置按以下优先级顺序生效（数字越小优先级越高，会被"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:19.710002Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "更高数字的配置覆盖）：\n1. 默认值：应用程序内硬编码的默认值。\n2. 系统默认文件：系统范围的默认设置，可被其他设置文件覆盖。\n3. 用户设置文件：当前用户的全局设置。\n4. 项目设置文件：项目特定的设置"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:20.329268Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "。\n5. 系统设置文件：系统范围的设置，覆盖所有其他设置文件。\n6. 环境变量：系统范围或会话特定的变量，可能从 .env 文件加载。\n7. 命令行参数：启动 CLI 时传递的值。\n\n命令行参数具有最高"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-26T03:56:20.965494Z"}
